title: Venture Brothers S03E11 [ORB] Preair - XviD
description:
Venture Brothers S03E11 [ORB] Preair - XviD	

TV : Adventure : DVD quality : English

Preair of the episode to be run August 10th. Includes before and after credit bits but no credits themselves. It should be fairly obvious to any regular fan of the show when those appear in the video. 

There is a scene missing though. About halfway through the episode is about 45 seconds of lost footage, which means you will have to tune into the Adult Swim show or Website when they become available to see this scene. The episode still makes sense without it and I have no idea what happens in it.
